{"tid":970543,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【原來咁紅】廣州處女開騷 洪卓立拖女上台冧到爆","createTime":"2019-01-06T02:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T05:37:57.000Z","uid":152123,"like":54,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9648a86885931856d52395c8acfd8b3ead41e263","tid":970543,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190104/large/1546591594_f6a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190104%2Flarge%2F1546591594_f6a0.jpg&h=b84043ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190104/large/1546591616_083e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190104%2Flarge%2F1546591616_083e.jpg&h=3598316f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190104/large/1546591598_7b32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190104%2Flarge%2F1546591598_7b32.jpg&h=35b4b04d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前，洪卓立（Ken）喺廣州體育館舉行演唱會，三千人場館全場爆滿。當晚除咗唱咗近三十首歌，Ken亦都有同歌迷玩遊戲，實行親親fans，最後佢仲公然拖女上台唱歌仔，期間二人十指緊扣、又深情對望，睇到台下觀眾嘩嘩聲。<br />\n<br />\n經常返內地商演嘅Ken喺廣東省有唔少歌迷，不過開show都係第一次，阿Ken話：「今次係我第一次嘅內地個人賣飛Live Band Concert，都幾緊張，一嚟係緊張自己嘅表現、二嚟就係緊張大家嘅反應。」不過佢嘅「緊張」隨住開場第一首歌一掃而空，「一出場、唱第一隻歌成個氣氛已經令我好感動，因為見到坐滿晒人。」話晒第一次開show，Ken當然有好多嘢想同歌迷分享，不過演唱會導演就叫Ken講少啲，「因為唔係成日見到內地嘅fans，所以會想同佢哋分享自己嘅嘢多啲，多啲，不過導演驚我一講就收唔到口，所以不停remind唔好咁多口水，哈哈。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然講唔到咁多嘢，但演唱會上都有同fans互動環節。演唱會中段除咗同fans玩估歌仔遊戲，尾段有遊戲，就係左右各一位觀眾喺台下試唱《難以取替》，得到掌聲較大嘅觀眾就可以上台同Ken合唱呢首歌最後一位女fans勝出上台，Ken亦都好識做，除咗不停放電，仲同佢十字緊扣，冧到個女fans暈得一陣陣，而台下fans嘅尖叫聲簡直震爆成個體育館。<br />\n<br />\n最後Encore時，Ken同全場大合唱佢嘅代表作《彌敦道》，氣氛高漲。之後着埋歌迷會會服嘅佢仲拎埋電話出嚟同大家玩selfie，整個演唱會圓滿結束。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>請珍惜洪卓立<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"1398c0a49afa808f4c07c1d1f50ccd30c5634cec","tid":970543,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:34:51.000Z","msg":"入到嚟居然重未睇到嗰句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d736da55368d3b97ad714c6b46ce8c43a6c0ee","tid":970543,"uid":196924,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:56:34.000Z","msg":"死人都識上廣州<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f796298928dd54079b700bf6ca12bec5e08e6fe","tid":970543,"uid":127347,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:58:09.000Z","msg":"復活立立"},{"pid":"e8fd56a89d9f617dd650cd995cb53da952ed0016","tid":970543,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:00:26.000Z","msg":"又係一個人板<br />\n此處不留人 自有留人處<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722300bc4cf4da45c55c12dca7dce776c495e8c9","tid":970543,"uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:01:52.000Z","msg":"支那都反而識得欣賞立立"},{"pid":"363c09309e7494294e94adf5099a00b785373b0f","tid":970543,"uid":25794,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:03:07.000Z","msg":"條女咩人"},{"pid":"67c8711f96e10c145fb76e27f268835f43c6e052","tid":970543,"uid":1067,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:03:15.000Z","msg":"陰間太多人與車　墳場鬧市人醉夜<br />\n害怕下棺等很久黑車　行汀九會快些"},{"pid":"180f584be98e7cbb099f1b6cb732d44428405f7f","tid":970543,"uid":87394,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:04:23.000Z","msg":"普通話講成點？<br />\n等個綜藝節目機會又可以起飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac0b83fb8196b452ef60eb13898caa4e208b3fc","tid":970543,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"363c09309e7494294e94adf5099a00b785373b0f","tid":970543,"uid":25794,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy"